OL,6,F1982 Channel 4 - the UK's fourth
OL,7,Fterrestrial TV channel - begins
OL,8,Fbroadcasting at 4.45pm. The first
OL,9,Fprogramme on the channel is Countdown.
OL,10,FRELATED ARTICLE: Countdown opening
OL,11,Ftitles/closing credits: first edition.
OL,13,F1984 The technicians strike at Thames
OL,14,FTelevision continues. A management-run
OL,15,Fservice is in operation. LWT comes on
OL,16,Fair this evening and broadcasts a full
OL,17,Fschedule on Saturday and Sunday.
